---
title: Greek Pastitsio Sausage and Pasta Bake with Zucchini and Creamy Sauce
description: This Greek take on lasagna is loaded with pasta, veggies, herby sausage and tomato sauce. All those layers are smothered and baked with a creamy, cheesy DIY sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pastitsio-grec-a-la-saucisse-et-aux-pates-89f2eee0.jpg
